high_descs: Turn left towards the tub.
Pick up the green sponge on the tub.
Take a step to the left.
Place the sponge in the tub.
Turn around, walk towards the wall, and then turn right to face the toilet.
Pick up the sponge on the toilet basin.
Turn right and walk towards the tub.
Place the sponge in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Place the two green sponges in the tub.

high_descs: Move to the tub to the left of you.
Pick up the sponge from the side of the tub.
Move to the center of the tub.
Place the sponge inside of the tub.
Move to the toilet behind and to the right of you.
Pick up the sponge from the toilet.
Move to the center of the tub to the right of you.
Place the sponge inside of the tub.
anns.task_desc: Put two sponges from the bathroom inside the tub.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the tub.
Pick up the green sponge from the edge of the tub.
Take one step to the left and then face the tub.
Place the sponge inside the tub.
Turn around and walk to the toilet.
Pick up the green sponge from the back of the toilet.
Turn right and walk to the tub.
Place the sponge next to the other sponge inside the tub.
anns.task_desc: Place two sponges inside the tub.

high_descs: Turn to your left and walk to reach the bathtub.
Pick up the sponge from the edge of the bathtub.
Look to the inside of the bathtub.
Place the sponge inside the bathtub.
Walk across the room until you reach the toilet on your right.
Grab the sponge from the top of the toilet.
Walk back to the bathtub.
Place the sponge inside the bathtub to the right of the other sponge.
anns.task_desc: Place two sponges in a bathtub.

high_descs: Turn left, go forward to the bath tub.
Take the sponge from the rim of the bath tub.
Move a step to the left.
Put the sponge in the bath tub to the left of the rag.
Turn around, go straight to the wall, turn right and go to the toilet.
Take the sponge from the top of the toilet tank.
Turn right, go forward to the bath tub.
Put the sponge to the right of the other sponge in the bath tub.
anns.task_desc: Put two sponges in a bath tub.
